{"profile":{"awsPrograms":[{"category":"Serverless Hero","joinedAt":2023.0,"memberStatus":"ACTIVE","programName":"HERO"}],"basicInfo":{"alias":"walmsles","avatar":"https://avatars.builderprofile.aws.dev/38QA46THCbzradbqPPXYRrRBwpM.webp","bio":"After 30 years of building software, I'm still on the tools - putting bugs in and taking them out, just like everyone else. I co-organize the Melbourne AWS Programming meetup, contribute to AWS Lambda Powertools (Python/TypeScript), and build open-source tooling including MCP servers for AWS documentation, CDK constructs, and serverless patterns published at ServerlessDNA.com.\n\nFocus Areas:\n* Serverless architecture patterns\n* Infrastructure as code with CDK\n* AI agent orchestration and MCP\n\nI share practical patterns and tooling to make serverless development more accessible to the community. \n\nAs an innovator and out-of-the-box thinker - it's software, anything is possible.","builderProfileId":"16ed6c7d-4e64-4ec1-afee-281bf8794f4f","createdOn":1.701306564608E12,"headline":"AWS Serverless Hero | Cloud Leader at Accenture","isStaff":false,"name":"Michael Walmsley"},"location":{"displayLocation":{"countryRegion":"AU","stateProvince":"VIC"}},"profileStatus":"ACTIVE","socials":{"blog":"https://serverlessdna.com","devto":"https://dev.to/walmsles","github":"https://github.com/walmsles","linkedIn":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/walmsles/","personal":"https://walmsles.dev","twitter":"https://x.com/walmsles","youtube":"https://www.youtube.com/@walmsles"}}}